title: sagarbansal21
author: sagarbansal21
content: AdLunam had an amazing discussion with yet another powerhouse CyberShakti in their recent episode of Future of NFTs. Cybershakti is the founder of the Haus of Shakti and a well known brand consultant, community builder and NFT artist. Cyber Shakti's work combines her travels, photography, glitch art, digital painting, and video loops into a beautifully layered combination. You can catch the recent episode on Spotify here: https://spoti.fi/3VeLhSL
